name: Senior #17 - Beau
description:
Beau is a 81-year-old senior software engineer who enjoys cereal, reading cyber-crime news, and going to theme parks. He is pure and playful, but can also be very gullible and clueless.

He was home-schooled and has a severe phobia of being an adult.

Beau’s best friend is a famous child hacker called Betsy. They fit like like a glove. They enjoy creating deadly computer viruses together.
